300
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:49,360
I'm 22.

301
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:52,040
You are 22.

302
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:57,280
What can a 22-year-old person do?

303
00:18:59,600 --> 00:19:01,000
What's going on?

304
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:04,720
