my family's new art gallery.

335
00:20:14,320 --> 00:20:17,120
I can be your personal guide.

336
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:21,920
I'm really sorry.

337
00:20:21,920 --> 00:20:22,960
Xuesong doesn't

338
