339
00:20:24,920 --> 00:20:27,320
He only likes to look at me.

340
00:20:27,800 --> 00:20:29,520
Am I right, Song?

341
00:20:31,040 --> 00:20:33,040
Yes. You are right.

342
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:35,240
So, sorry

343
00:20:35,240 --> 00:20:36,880
