346
00:20:40,240 --> 00:20:42,520
See you next time. Bye.

347
00:20:44,160 --> 00:20:45,200
I'm sorry.

348
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:47,000
I probably can't visit

349
00:20:48,320 --> 00:20:50,640
your art gallery. Please excuse me.

