a wine business.

355
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:15,680
But you are not that bad either.

356
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:20,560
This is nothing.

357
00:21:20,560 --> 00:21:22,760
When I was at home,

358
00:21:23,320 --> 00:21:25,480
I drank at least
eight to ten bottles at least.

359
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:27,520
Don't you know

360
