00:22:34,520 --> 00:22:35,280
Xia.

383
00:22:36,480 --> 00:22:38,320
Hui is my son.

384
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:39,640
I can tell

385
00:22:39,640 --> 00:22:41,040
