556
00:35:22,080 --> 00:35:23,480
You.

557
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:25,640
Who ate the breakfast I made?

558
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:29,280
Me.

559
00:35:29,280 --> 00:35:30,520
So,

560
00:35:30,520 --> 00:35:32,760
